Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.10,0:00:12.73,Header,,0,0,0,,{\fade(158,0)\i1}Snack World, the hallowed ground\Nof dreams and adventures.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.35,0:00:18.82,Header,,0,0,0,,{\fade(158,0)\i1}A world full of dragons, smartphones,\Nand convenience stores.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.65,0:00:22.07,Header,,0,0,0,,{\fade(158,0)\i1}It's a pretty cool place!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.99,0:00:25.36,Header,,0,0,0,,{\fade(158,0)\i1}But like any world, it has a villain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.28,0:00:28.20,Header,,0,0,0,,{\fade(158,0)\i1}Vinegar Khan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.41,0:00:33.96,Header,,0,0,0,,{\fade(158,0)\i1}He is an evil merchant who has taken\Neverything from our young hero, Chup.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.42,0:00:39.59,Header,,0,0,0,,{\fade(158,0)\i1}And so, the boy embarks on a\Nreckless journey for revenge!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.17,0:00:42.21,Header,,0,0,0,,{\fade(158,0)\i1}What perils await him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.88,0:00:46.59,Header,,0,0,0,,{\fade(158,0)\i1}The answer lies in his...destiny.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.52,0:01:04.57,EPTITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fade(290,462)\pos(641.6,556.4)\fscx108\fscy108\frx8\fry0}Ep. 5: The Desert Kraken
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.94,0:01:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Princess Melora moaning]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.16,0:01:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I want it, I want it, I want it~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.29,0:01:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there, my little Melora. I hear you, I hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to divert this request to Chup now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.05,0:01:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Melora, what's got you talking so weirdly?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.25,0:01:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She's getting eyelash extensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.25,0:01:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They're still drying, so she can't open her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.59,0:01:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mhm, I've been thinking of growing out my eyelashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.88,0:01:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Err, and probably my hair too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But why are you doing this {\i1}now{\i0}?\NDoesn't it seem extremely rude?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.98,0:01:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Melora's kissy face...is really fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.68,0:01:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I-if I were to end up kissing Princess Melora...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That face would be... {\i1}[cackling]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.12,0:01:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so deluded?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.83,0:02:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,After all...you could say a princess with no make-up would be a crisis!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A "make-up-less battle," perhaps!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say one needs skin to shine from the inside, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I want daddy to get me the Ultimate Moisturizing Cream! Mwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.60,0:02:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oink...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I got an air kiss from Princess Melora!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.50,0:02:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That should explain it, Chup.
