Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.23,0:02:26.00,Quest,,0,0,0,,{\fade(50,0)\frz6.813\fscx134\fscy176\pos(668,244)}Get the Ultimate Moisturizing Cream
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.23,0:02:26.00,Quest,,0,0,0,,{\fade(50,0)\fscx196\fscy205\pos(140,256)\frz6.813\c&H494845&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur13\bord5}Quest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.23,0:02:26.00,Quest,,0,0,0,,{\fade(50,0)\frz6.813\fscx134\fscy176\pos(668,244)\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur15}Get the Ultimate Moisturizing Cream
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can collect the Ultimate\NMoisturizing Cream from the Kraken.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just like you, Minster, so smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kraken...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.41,0:02:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohoho, I got it that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.03,0:02:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kraken? Hm, that's the squid monster\Nwith a bunch of twisting legs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So we should head off to the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it'll be in the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The desert?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kraken lives in the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.41,0:02:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It often attacks the oasis and steals its water.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.93,0:02:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would it be doing that in the desert?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it make more sense for a squid to live in the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...maybe it has a motive behind that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.81,0:03:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, that trivial matter is not of our understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.80,0:03:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving on, head towards that desert!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.69,0:03:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The means behind this request feel off...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trusting you with this, Chup!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ur- yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That was just a delayed reaction!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmmm...mwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.49,0:03:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh...this time, I'll fully, flawlessly catch it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it for Princess Meloraaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- Goodness, you're so desperate!\N- Oink...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,First order of business, we need\Nweapons to take down Kraken.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.32,0:03:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kraken-striking weapons, weapons...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What's this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- {\i1}[Vinegar Khan laughing]{\i0}\N- Vinegar Shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh, Vinegar...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Time is money!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let Vinegar tell you how spendin' money is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, joy! Oh, boy! Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.07,0:03:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for Vinegar Shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.19,0:04:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I present to you today, the Crystal Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks fascinating!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is {\i1}the{\i0} Crystal Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, it's epic...but!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Man shrieks]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Vinegar Corp. has prepared {\i1}this{\i0} for the occasion!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll boost your ATK!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The amazing Crystal Sword just got even amazing-er!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Introducing the Crystal Sword Z!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How d'ya like {\i1}this{\i0} brilliance?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.64,0:04:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ya want it? Don'tcha just wanna have it for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Vinegar cackling]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Chup...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.78,0:04:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a good look, you can even slash through apples!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Slashin' through radishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, you can even slash right through\Nsomething turned to stone by Medusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,M-mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.59,0:04:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh...I'm hungry, mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:05:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Chup, you really want it that bad? Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.48,0:05:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Your stew is fully, flawlessly the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.97,0:05:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so? That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.06,0:05:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- I wanna have this tomorrow too!\N- Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How about tomorrow {\i1}and{\i0} the day after?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hehe, alright. I'll always be there to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Always being able to have my mom's food...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.04,0:05:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought those days would never end...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.54,0:05:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All of that...all of that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.59,0:05:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All of that was ruined by Vinegar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.05,0:05:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In need of a lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hahahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.01,0:05:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get revenge against Vinegar, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oink!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, right now! Straight to the desert!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oi, slow down, Chu-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you trying to cover yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.52,0:05:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to calm down, Chup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oink...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We still haven't gotten weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad, I started getting tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, it's likely that this spell might\Nbe effective against Kraken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:04.16,Header,,0,0,0,,"Bone-Dry" "{\fs(38)}▼{\fs(46)} Effect"\N"This spell, when used, will cause all of the water in the opponent's\Nbody to go dry at once. As a result ..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"Bone-Dry?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mr. Carbonara!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.74,0:06:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chup!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If it isn't the disappointing as ever chums entering a store with a Level F aura. 'Sup?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And aren't {\i1}you{\i0} a blabbermouth like usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Unable to recognize voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.09,0:06:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.09,0:06:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what brings you here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to buy a spell called "Bone-Dry".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Bone-Dry, huh? An unusual thing to buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, if I'm not mistaken, it should be on the back shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinocchio, help me look for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.95,0:06:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man! That's an awful lot of Snacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.74,0:06:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Mr. Carbonara, which one is Bone-Dry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that one must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.25,0:06:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.49,0:06:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...and it looks like the labels stuck on wore off too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.58,0:07:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know which one is Bone-Dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Well, what do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.64,0:07:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,May I suggest trying them out one-by-one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that alright with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll do for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you can't buy a spell if you don't know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Sounds like fun, I'll give it a go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Nothing happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go shooting any more spells, Chup...wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this raspy voice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayone, your voice is acting up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Chup guffawing]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like instead of a "Bone-Dry"\Nspell, it was a "Hi-Fi" spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Haha...guess it was wrong. Here, let's try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Click!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- Cast!\N- Ah, careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A-ah...huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, Pepperon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A-a-ahh, my head feels all dizzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:08:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like this one was an "Outcry" spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- {\i1}[Pepperon groaning]{\i0}\N- Ow! Move over, Pepperon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm deeply sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah, that smarts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.86,0:08:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Groaning]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.43,0:08:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, this time for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- Here!\N- Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo! Feelin' wild here tonight, whazzup?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Check it out, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang, he's acting flashy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be the "Amplify" spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, little lady, feelin' pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna exchange e-mails? Hehehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Something about this feels wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a raspy voice, {\i1}that's{\i0} what feels wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.59,0:08:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You really ain't doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaagh, the dizziness won't stop, aah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Chup, hurry up and look for the right one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.94,0:08:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be it! Let's try it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-whaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's THIS?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.78,0:08:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- We're mullets!\N- Mullets?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Saltwater fish that live in the ocean near estuaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen them swim towards surface water in schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- That can't be!\N- Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopping around to move feels annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't settle my posture!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.65,0:09:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit of a stretch, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You could call it the "Walleye" spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oink!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Butako, wait, don't!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oink, oink~!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah, Butako, stop! They aren't delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away from us!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Pepperon yelping]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My leg keeps bending!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oink!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.31,0:09:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Chup, why are you just standing there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.77,0:09:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oink!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.55,0:09:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so tired of the Walleye spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.29,0:09:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[All gasping]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glittering, I'm dazzling!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all sparkly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- The "Beautify" spell.\N- Beautify spell!! ...Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.05,0:09:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oi, why do you look so happy about this? It's so radiant...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.05,0:09:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh...I can't even see anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, but the idea of me having a sparkling\Ncharacter just moves me so much!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:09:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- I've got it! I've got it!\N- Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the "Bone-Dry" spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- Really?\N- You bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.35,0:10:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, we might want to test it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.46,0:10:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh..ah...I suddenly feel so parched...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.08,0:10:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, that's the Bone-Dry spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah...w-water please...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.53,0:10:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be 10 gillan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you take gold?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, do you want water or no?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I want it...I want it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.22,0:10:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Chup sighs]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.31,0:10:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What an awful experience...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who's talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Given that you've been casting all those spells on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But hey, we bought the Bone-Dry spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wild! There's one of them Hero Marts here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we go to the desert, let's get\Nourselves some water! Check it out, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, whazzup?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.20,0:10:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why haven't the effects of that\Nspell worn off Gob-san yet...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:10:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And only the first one he got.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be his age?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, maybe he'll come back two\Ndays later with muscular pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that guy's acting like that from age?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Whazzup? Yo, yo, check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He sure has his ways of acting perfectly\Nlike a flashy kid for such an old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.89,0:11:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Grunting]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Kraken?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- You find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.90,0:11:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be Mermaid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.95,0:11:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mermaid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What would a sea-dwelling Monster be doing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Chup, that's a monster, are you sure\Nyou're feeling up to fight so suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just gonna try to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows, she might have info on the Kraken.
