Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.56,0:12:01.27,MonsterName,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,500)\c&HA75D12&\frz8.96\fscx299\fscy294\pos(326,226)\bord20\3c&HE7E6E6&\clip(m 186 244 l 206 234 258 222 276 236 494 222 532 174 572 168 574 82 444 66 132 152 88 160 82 92 598 20 620 284 170 268)}Mermaid
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, you!\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, privacy, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Err, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.22,0:12:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Privacy, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But, the Kraken...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.61,0:12:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! What don't you get about "privacy, please?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.98,0:12:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You still think it's worth it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She's clearly not listening to us, so let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- We're not going anywhere!\N- ...What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like my grandmother says!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Listening is a temporary disgrace, like Keanu is Reeves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He signs with an oil-based pen!
