Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.21,0:12:26.92,Proverb,,0,0,0,,{\ko3}{\2aFF\fscx58\fscy68\pos(246,142)\frz357.6}H{\ko3}e{\ko7} s{\ko3}i{\ko3}g{\ko3}n{\ko3}s{\ko7} w{\ko3}i{\ko4}t{\ko7}h {\ko3}a{\ko4}n{\ko14}\N{\ko6}o{\ko7}i{\ko6}l{\ko7}-{\ko6}b{\ko6}a{\ko6}s{\ko6}e{\ko12}d {\ko6}p{\ko6}e{\ko6}n{\ko6}.{\ko118}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:26.92,Proverb,,0,0,0,,{\frz357.6\pos(116,496)\fscx93\fscy94}-Tome
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes sense you'd use a specific pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, you want my signature, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what the heck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Being popular sure is tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- {\i1}[Gob-san grunts]{\i0}\N- There! Signed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.59,0:12:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If you put this up for online auction,\Nyou'll get crushed in every way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.61,0:12:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I came to the oasis\Njust to get away from fans...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:13:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess my overflowing idol aura just can't be concealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's just fate for the top idol of the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't live with a loss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All you fans out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to today's Mermaid concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Giggles]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.68,0:13:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oho!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me hear the energy in your voices! {\i1}Yay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Pepperon mumbles]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? I can't heeeear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be shy! 1...2...Yay!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.77,0:13:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[All mumbling]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.94,0:13:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooraaaay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why so quiet? One more time! {\i1}Yay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is! {\i1}Yay!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,3rd level seats, you ready?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaaay!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,2nd level seats, you ready?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaaaay!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.72,0:14:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All good? Come on, arena!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Yay!! Yaaaay!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know Pepperon liked this sort of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She's probably not even going to listen to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we just go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Holding a concert really is the best!\NThank you, everyone, I love you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Yay! Yay! Yay! Yay! Yay! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All this excitement's got my throat dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,On that note...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,W-what? Why did the mood here suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.41,0:14:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You three will give me every moist belonging you have! Yay!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaa- {\i1}[Gargles]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[All gargling]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Your moist belongings!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.55,0:14:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna drown!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't counterattack with this water pressure...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.27,0:14:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Chup! Butako can fight with her fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Butako-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oink...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Butako's drowning with the water in her nose...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh, I can't help it. Here, some water!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it, Mermaid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.87,0:15:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Gasping for breath]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's far from enough!\NI'll need some more from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...don't!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please gimme more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Please gimme more!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.63,0:15:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- Aah, no!\N- More, more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Gob-san, quick, the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave her all I had before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.67,0:15:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, since it's come to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,More!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so persistent towards me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cuz, if I attack boys, won't my fans quit me when they find out? Hehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mermaid!\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We've brought every moist belonging we have on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.58,0:15:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A used tissue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A used sock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:16:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, the worst kinds of moist...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.47,0:16:02.97,Header,,0,0,0,,"Keiko Campbell"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:05.15,Header,,0,0,0,,"Come again, Gobby. -Keiko Campbell"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,"Come again, Gobby. -Keiko Campbell"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Moist like water, not moist like a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Here! Take it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.14,0:16:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...well...n-no thanks, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I- I can't accept handmade gifts\Nwithout talking to my manager, haha...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.11,0:16:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayone, now! Use the Bone-Dry spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Bone-Dry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Noooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I have wrinkles around my eye... Ca...can\Nsomeone refer me to a beauty salon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Sighs]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.21,0:16:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Snap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Chuckles]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We got Mermaid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Man...that sure wore me out a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I glimpsed the dark side of an idol's public image...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:55.98,Location,,0,0,0,,{\fade(525,525)\pos(640,658)}Kraken's Dwelling
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:17:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mermaid said that the Kraken\Nlived somewhere around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She sure was a halfhearted idol...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We might be better off looking somewhere else...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- You good with that?\N- Yeah, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Kraken roaring]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- Aah!\N- Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be Kraken!
