Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Frightening...gigantic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Roaring]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wooden Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your choice for adventure, Qloris!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.40,0:17:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wooden Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.36,0:17:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Lookin' good, Pepperon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.90,0:17:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi-yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hnng... Take this! Yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.41,0:17:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! That didn't work out for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's what you want, get a\Ntaste of my strongest spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.92,0:18:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayone, use Bone-Dry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.17,0:18:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this, Kraken...Bone-Dry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.20,0:18:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Kraken groaning]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurrah! You took down the Kraken!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We've won!
