Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure was an easy win, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.99,0:20:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But it {\i1}is{\i0} a big dried squid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.95,0:20:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure if we grill this baby, it'll taste like heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.88,0:20:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A full, flawless victory for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.92,0:20:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hehe!\N- Oink!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- However...\N- Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In this condition, how are we supposed to\Nobtain the Ultimate Moisturizing Cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.39,0:20:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- Whaa?\N- Oink...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.85,0:20:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me get this straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Were we {\i1}not{\i0} supposed to dry up the Kraken like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah, this is bad! What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.74,0:20:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mermaid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:43.75,Marine,,0,0,0,,Marine! Marine, marine! Marine, marine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.25,0:20:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how bothersome...I was hoping\Nfor some privacy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.13,0:20:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mermaid, use your water attack to hydrate the Kraken!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, why would you leave that kind of work to an idol?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.21,0:21:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Please? I'll even cheer you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll look at your website!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.96,0:21:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what the heck! I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.98,0:21:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also the fate of an idol to\Nmake her fan's wishes come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.53,0:21:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go! Are you ready? Yay! Yay, yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's get this show on the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Desert Kraken, you feeling lively?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Kraken groaning]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.75,0:21:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaat? I can't hear you! Alright then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Have some more water!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay, yay, yay-yay-yay, yay-yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, hold on, don't you think you're\Ngoing a bit far with the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.76,0:21:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaaay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.02,0:21:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Kraken roaring]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.94,0:21:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay, yay, yaaay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.44,0:21:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Roaring]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.33,0:21:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys think he looks livelier than before?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.45,0:22:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay, yaaay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.53,0:22:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[All screaming]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.87,0:22:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Kraken groaning]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.18,0:22:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh...I'm all dark, sticky, and I smell like fish...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.12,0:22:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help but wonder if this squid ink is the cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds like something to {\i1}ink{\i0} about!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.09,0:22:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We sure showed that monster we're not {\i1}squiddin'!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.01,0:22:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha! Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.09,0:22:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make a squid pun too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That battle was {\i1}inkredible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.85,0:22:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That actually wasn't half-bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.73,0:22:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Seafood sure is ex-{\i1}squid{\i0}-sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.56,0:22:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, {\i1}barnacles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.31,0:22:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is {\i1}kraken{\i0} me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.95,0:22:48.62,MonsterName,,0,0,0,,{\c&H8C5ED4&\bord2\pos(542,376)}Mayone's Snack World Course
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.62,0:23:09.98,MonsterName,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE9E7E0&\bord2\fs70\pos(450,574)}"Britannia Enchant"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.87,0:22:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mayone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.90,0:22:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you teaching us about today?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.70,0:22:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's about Britannia Enchant!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.87,0:22:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs(45)}Britannia Enchant is a luxury brand made for experienced wizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.04,0:22:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They make magical weapons and armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.12,0:23:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They're very popular with adventurers, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.37,0:23:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Chup's equipped with a Crystal Sword from Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.13,0:23:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! I've got the coolest weapon!
