Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.24,0:23:24.87,Quest,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(640,480)\3c&H09F1E9&\bord3\fade(485,0)\blur10}The Cutlass That Can Tear Anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.27,0:23:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There exists a sword that can cut through anything in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We can definitely take down the Kraken with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.06,0:23:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: "The Cutlass That Can Tear Anything?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.77,0:23:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, it's time for a big adventure!
